#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "Administration Handbook"
msgstr "Priručnik za administratore"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&gcompris; is a rich educational software suite which contains a wide range "
"of activities."
msgstr ""
"&gcompris; je kvalitetan obrazovni softverski paket koji sadrži širok "
"spektar raznolikih aktivnosti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It offers various activities aimed at covering a variety of fields. The "
"topics include reading and typing, arithmetics, geography, sciences, and "
"other topics. It is meant to be used both at home and at school."
msgstr ""
"Nudi razne aktivnosti usmjerene u različitim područjima. Teme uključuju "
"čitanje i tipkanje, aritmetiku, geografiju, znanost i drugo. Namijenjen je "
"za korištenje kod kuće ali i u školi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The purpose of &gcompris; is to provide playful activities but always "
"educational."
msgstr ""
"Svrha &gcompris; je pružiti razigrane aktivnosti te istovremeno obrazovati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&gcompris; is part of &kde; project and is placed under the <ulink url="
"\"https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.html\">AGPLv3 license</ulink>. All "
"the code, except the engine for analog electricity activity is under <ulink "
"url=\"https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl.html\">GPLv3 license</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"&gcompris; dio je projekta &kde; i nalazi se pod <ulink url=\"https://www."
"gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.html\">licencom AGPLv3</ulink>. Svi kodovi, osim "
"simulatora za električnu energiju, su pod <ulink url=\"https://www.gnu.org/"
"licenses/gpl.html\">GPLv3 licencom</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&gcompris; is available on the following operating systems: &GNU;/&Linux;, "
"&BSD;, &macOS;, &Windows;, Android. It requires a 3D card with support of "
"<emphasis>OpenGL 2.1</emphasis> or higher. 32 bits color depth is mandatory."
msgstr ""
"&gcompris; dostupan je na sljedećim operacijskim sustavima: &GNU;/&Linux;, "
"&BSD;, &macOS;, &Windows; i Android. Potrebna je 3D kartica s podrškom za "
"<emphasis>OpenGL 2.1</emphasis> ili noviji. Obavezna dubina boje je najmanje "
"32-bita."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "Installation"
msgstr "Instalacija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The software is delivered under several forms. Follow the process according "
"to your case."
msgstr ""
"Softver se isporučuje u nekoliko varijanti. Za svaku varijantu opisan je "
"postupak."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&GNU;/&Linux;: use the packages delivered by your &GNU;/&Linux; "
"distribution. If &gcompris; is not packaged in your &Linux; distribution, "
"please contact them to ask for the inclusion of &gcompris;."
msgstr ""
"&GNU;/&Linux;: koristi pakete koje su isporučene uz tvoju &GNU;/&Linux; "
"distribuciju. Ako &gcompris; nije sadržan u &Linux; distribuciji, javite se "
"distributeru kako bi zatražili uključivanje &gcompris;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&Windows;: delivered under a classic installer for &Windows; or via the "
"Microsoft Store."
msgstr ""
"&Windows;: isporučuje se kao klasični instalacijski programa za &Windows; "
"ili putem Microsoftove trgovine."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid "&macOS;: delivered under a classic installer."
msgstr "&macOS;: isporučuje se kao klasični instalacijski program."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Android: distributed by the F-Droid store or Google Play Store. APK file is "
"also available."
msgstr ""
"Android: distribuira ga F-Droid trgovina ili Google Play trgovina. Dostupna "
"je i APK datoteka."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "The User Interface"
msgstr "Korisničko sučelje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The interface is designed for easy use by small children. &gcompris; is "
"controlled with a mouse. Keyboard navigation is also available on most of "
"the activities."
msgstr ""
"Sučelje je dizajnirano kako bi ga i mala djeca mogla koristiti. Aplikacijom "
"&gcompris; se upravlja putem miša. Navigacija tipkovnicom dostupna je "
"također u većini aktivnosti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "Main window"
msgstr "Početni prozor"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start the program, &gcompris; shows a graphical interface which "
"presents the list of activities with a control bar at the bottom."
msgstr ""
"Kada pokreneš program, &gcompris; prikazuje grafičko sučelje s prikazom "
"popisa aktivnosti i upravljačkom trakom na dnu."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here’s a screenshot of &gcompris; main window"
msgstr "Snimka zaslona &gcompris; Početni prozor"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "&gcompris; Main Window"
msgstr "&gcompris; Početni prozor"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each icon represents an activity. Around each one, you can find small icons "
"which give additional information about the activity. A simple click on the "
"icon will lead you to an activity or a menu of activities. There are 8 "
"sections (categories) of activities, which are placed on the top or on the "
"left (only if your orientation is portrait). For example, there is section "
"“Board Games”, which includes board games, like Chess, Tic-Tac-Toe or Align "
"Four."
msgstr ""
"Svaka ikona predstavlja aktivnost. U gornjem lijevom kutu nalaze se "
"zvjezdice s dodatnom informacijom o težini aktivnosti. Klik na ikonu dovesti "
"će vas do aktivnosti ili izbornika aktivnosti. Postoji 8 sekcija "
"(kategorija) aktivnosti, koje su smještene na vrhu ili lijevo (samo ako vam "
"je orijentacija portret). Na primjer, postoji sekcija \"Strategija\", koji "
"uključuje društvene igre poput šaha, križić-kružića ili 4 u nizu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some categories have subcategories to better filter the activities. For math "
"activities, we have three subcategories: numeration, arithmetic and measures."
msgstr ""
"Neke kategorije imaju potkategorije radi boljeg grupiranja aktivnosti. Za "
"matematičke aktivnosti imamo tri potkategorije: računanje, aritmetiku i "
"mjere."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "The stars indicate the age group for which each game is designed:"
msgstr "Zvjezdice označavaju dobnu skupinu kojoj je aktivnost namijenjena:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "1, 2 or 3 yellow stars — for 2 to 6 years old."
msgstr "1, 2 ili 3 žute zvjezdice — od 2 do 6 godina."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid "1, 2 or 3 red stars — greater than 6 years old."
msgstr "1, 2 ili 3 crvene zvijezdice — starije od 6 godina."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the bottom of the screen there is a control bar for &gcompris;. The "
"possible icons are (the icons are only displayed if they are available in "
"the activity):"
msgstr ""
"Na dnu zaslona nalazi se upravljačka traka. Moguće ikone su (prikazuju se "
"samo ako su dostupne u aktivnosti):"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid "Home — Leaves the current activity, returns to the previous menu."
msgstr "Kućica - napušta trenutnu aktivnost, vraća se na prethodni izbornik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"“OK” — Validate, confirm your answer. Some activities do not detect "
"automatically whether or not the child has completed the task. In this case, "
"you have to click on this icon. You can also use the &Enter; key on your "
"keyboard."
msgstr ""
"\"OK\" — validiraj, potvrdi tvoj odgovor. Koriste se za aktivnosti koje ne "
"prepoznaju da je dijete dovršilo zadatak. U tom slučaju dijete mora kliknuti "
"na ovu ikonu. Na tipkovnici možeš koristiti i tipku &Enter;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Light — Display a hint for the activity. We can help the children on some "
"activities to guide them to find the answers."
msgstr ""
"Žarulja — prikaži savjet za aktivnost. Savjeti mogu pomoći djeci u nekim "
"aktivnostima kao vid usmjeravanja prema rješenju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Arrows — The present level is displayed. Click on one of the arrows to "
"select another level. Generally, the activities offer several levels whose "
"numbers depend on the activity. In &gcompris;, it is possible to go to the "
"next level without having completed the current level."
msgstr ""
"Strelice — prikazuje se trenutna razina aktivnosti. Klikom na jednu od "
"strelica mijenja se razina. Aktivnosti nude izbor nekoliko razina. "
"&gcompris; omogućuje prijelaz na višu razinu i bez završetka trenutne razine."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lips — Ask &gcompris; to repeat the question."
msgstr "Usne — &gcompris; će ponoviti pitanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Question mark — Display the help dialog box. Sometimes, an activity can be "
"too complex to be described easily in the description area. In this case, "
"this function gives access to additional information."
msgstr ""
"Upitnik — prikaz dijaloškog okvira pomoći. Ponekad aktivnost može biti "
"previše složena da bi se ukratko opisala. U tom slučaju ova funkcija daje "
"pristup dodatnim informacijama."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tool box — Configuration menu. The configuration is saved in the user "
"repository (folder) under the name <filename>.config/gcompris/gcompris-qt."
"conf</filename>. This is a text file which can be edited manually."
msgstr ""
"Alatka — konfiguracijski izbornik. Konfiguracija se sprema u korisničku mapu "
"pod nazivom <filename>.config/gcompris/gcompris-qt.conf</filename>. Ovo je "
"tekstualna datoteka i može se ručno uređivati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"List item — Display the activity settings menu. There are two possible tabs "
"here. First one, “Dataset”, allows to choose the levels of the activities "
"depending on several objectives and the second one, “Options”, allows to "
"update the configuration of the activity if available."
msgstr ""
"Stavke popisa — prikaz izbornika postavki aktivnosti. Ovdje postoje dvije "
"moguće kartice: \"Skup podataka\" omogućuje odabir razina aktivnosti ovisno "
"o nekoliko ciljeva dok \"Opcije\" omogućuju ažuriranje konfiguracije "
"aktivnosti ako je dostupna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Capital “G” — Information box on &gcompris;, presents the main contributors "
"and the version of the software."
msgstr ""
"Veliko slovo G — informacije o &gcompris;, aplikaciji s popisom ključnih "
"suradnika i verzijom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Power — Quit &gcompris;. You can also use the shortcut on your keyboard "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Napajanje — isključuje &gcompris;. Možeš koristiti i prečac na tipkovnici "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid "Kiosk Mode"
msgstr "Kiosk način rada"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you use &gcompris; with small children or on a self-service kiosk, you "
"can disable a certain number of options:"
msgstr ""
"Kada &gcompris; koriste mala djeca ili se nalazi na samouslužnom kiosku, "
"možeš onemogućiti određene funkcionalnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput><command>gcompris --enable-kioskmode</command></userinput>: "
"disable the <guiicon>Quit</guiicon> and <guiicon>Configuration</guiicon> "
"buttons."
msgstr ""
"<userinput><command>gcompris --enable-kioskmode</command></userinput>: "
"onemogućuje gumbe za <guiicon>izlaz</guiicon> i <guiicon>konfiguraciju</"
"guiicon>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput><command>gcompris --disable-kioskmode</command></userinput>: "
"enable the <guiicon>Quit</guiicon> and <guiicon>Configuration</guiicon> "
"buttons."
msgstr ""
"<userinput><command>gcompris --disable-kioskmode</command></userinput>: "
"onemogućuje gumbe za <guiicon>izlaz</guiicon> i <guiicon>konfiguraciju</"
"guiicon>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput><command>gcompris -f</command></userinput>: run &gcompris; in "
"fullscreen mode"
msgstr ""
"<userinput><command>gcompris -f</command></userinput>: pokreće &gcompris; u "
"prikazu preko cijelog zaslona"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput><command>gcompris -C</command></userinput>: disable the cursor "
"(touch screen mode)"
msgstr ""
"<userinput><command>gcompris -C</command></userinput>: onemogućuje pokazivač "
"(u slučaju kada se koristi zaslon osjetljiv na dodir)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid "These options can of course be combined."
msgstr "Ove se opcije, naravno, mogu kombinirati."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keyboard Shortcuts"
msgstr "Tipkovni prečaci"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shortcut"
msgstr "Prečac"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Action"
msgstr "Akcija"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Esc; or <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo>"
msgstr ""
"&Esc; ili <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quit the current activity or dialog then return to the main menu."
msgstr ""
"Zatvori trenutnu aktivnost ili dijalog, a zatim se vrati na glavni izbornik."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quit &gcompris; without further notice."
msgstr "Zatvori &gcompris; bez ikakvih obavijesti."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toggle fullscreen mode."
msgstr "Uključi/isključi načina prikaza preko cijelog zaslona."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>M</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>M</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toggle sound mute."
msgstr "Uključi/isključi zvuk."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>B</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>B</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display or hide the control bar."
msgstr "Prikaži ili sakrij kontrolnu traku."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid "Notes on Internationalization"
msgstr "Napomene o lokalizaciji"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&gcompris; is internationalized and is available in more than 35 languages. "
"If you want to check if your language is available, you can start &gcompris; "
"and select your language in the option of configuration."
msgstr ""
"&gcompris; je lokaliziran i dostupan je na više od 35 jezika. Ako želiš "
"provjeriti je li i tvoj jezik dostupan, pokreni &gcompris; i odaberi jezik u "
"konfiguraciji."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Be careful, some languages need specific fonts to be displayed correctly."
msgstr ""
"No pazi, neki jezici trebaju određene fontove kako bi se ispravno prikazali."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If your language is not supported, you can contribute to the software and "
"add the translation of your language. If you are interested, you can contact "
"the <ulink url=\"https://l10n.kde.org/teams\">translation team</ulink> of "
"the &kde; project for your language. You can check the level of translation "
"for your language on the <ulink url=\"https://l10n.kde.org/\">&kde; "
"translation web site</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Ako tvoj jezik nije podržan, možeš ga prevesti. Ako si zainteresiran, možeš "
"se obratiti <ulink url=\"https://l10n.kde.org/teams\">prevoditeljskom timu</"
"ulink> projekta &kde; tvog jezika. Aktualni status prijevoda možeš "
"provjeriti na web mjestu <ulink url=\"https://l10n.kde.org/\">&kde; "
"lokalizacija</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid "Language learning"
msgstr "Učenje jezika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use &gcompris; in a foreign language that you are learning. Select a "
"foreign language in the configuration menu. Do not forget to download the "
"optional audio modules for this language."
msgstr ""
"Možeš koristiti &gcompris; i na stranom jeziku kojeg želiš naučiti. Dovoljno "
"je u konfiguraciji odabrati željeni strani jezik. Ne zaboravi preuzeti i "
"dodatne zvučne zapise za izabrani jezik."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid "Customizing activities"
msgstr "Prilagodba aktivnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can customize some activities using the configuration button in them. "
"For example, you can set the locale in some text activities (like "
"wordsgame), or make it show real car images instead of filled rectangles "
"(traffic)."
msgstr ""
"Neke aktivnosti možeš prilagoditi pomoću gumba za konfiguraciju koje se "
"nalaze unutar aktivnosti. Na primjer, možeš postaviti regionalnu shemu u "
"nekim tekstualnim aktivnostima (kao što je primjerice Igra riječi) ili "
"učiniti da se prikazuju stvarne fotografije automobila umjesto ispunjenih "
"pravokutnika (promet)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For multiple activities, you can choose several datasets in the "
"configuration. Each one has a specific objective which is described."
msgstr ""
"Kod nekih aktivnosti možeš u konfiguraciji odabrati različite skupove "
"podataka. Svaki od njih ima određeni cilj koji je jasno naveden."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
