#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid "Console Parameters"
msgstr "Parametri naredbene konzole"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Running &gcompris; from a command console with the “--help” option will "
"display all the parameters it accepts:"
msgstr ""
"Ako pokreneš &gcompris; s naredbene konzole pomoću opcije --help prikazati "
"će se svi parametre koje prihvaća:"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid "-f, --fullscreen"
msgstr "-f, --fullscreen"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid "Run &gcompris; in fullscreen mode."
msgstr "Pokreni &gcompris; u prikazu preko cijelog zaslona."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:268
#, no-c-format
msgid "-w, --window"
msgstr "-w, --window"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid "Run &gcompris; in window mode."
msgstr "Pokreni &gcompris; u prozoru."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid "-s, --sound"
msgstr "-s, --sound"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid "Run &gcompris; with sound enabled."
msgstr "Pokreni &gcompris; s uključenim zvukom."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid "-m, --mute"
msgstr "-m, --mute"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid "Run &gcompris; without sound."
msgstr "Pokreni &gcompris; bez zvuka."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid "-c, --cursor"
msgstr "-c, --cursor"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid "Run &gcompris; with the default system cursor."
msgstr "Pokreni &gcompris; sa zadanim pokazivačem sustava."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid "-C, --nocursor"
msgstr "-C, --nocursor"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:285
#, no-c-format
msgid "Run &gcompris; without cursor (touch screen mode)."
msgstr ""
"Pokreni &gcompris; bez pokazivača (način zaslona osjetljivog na dodir)."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid "-v, --version"
msgstr "-v, --version"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid "Print the version of &gcompris;."
msgstr "Prikaži verziju &gcompris;."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "-l, --list-activities"
msgstr "-l, --list-activities"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid "Outputs all the available activities on the standard output."
msgstr "Prikaži sve dostupne aktivnosti na standardnom izlazu."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid "--launch activity"
msgstr "--launch activity"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:297
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specify the activity when starting &gcompris;."
msgstr "Odaberi polaznu aktivnost kada se pokreće &gcompris;."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid "--start-level level"
msgstr "--start-level razina"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specify the level on which to start the activity specified by “--launch” "
"option when starting &gcompris;. Ignored if no “--launch” option, or if "
"level specified is invalid."
msgstr ""
"Prilikom pokretanja GComprisa odredi razinu na kojoj želiš započeti "
"aktivnost zadanu pomoću \"--launch\". Postavka će biti zanemarena ukoliko se "
"ne koristi \"--launch\" ili ako navedena razina ne postoji."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid "--difficulty {value|min-max}"
msgstr "--difficulty {value|min-max}"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For the session, force &gcompris; activities difficulty to be either at "
"value or between min and max values. The values must be between 1 and 6, and "
"if the format is min-max, the min value must be lower than the max value. If "
"it is not the case &gcompris; will not start."
msgstr ""
"Za pokrenutu sesiju forsiraj da razina &gcompris; aktivnosti bude na "
"određenoj vrijednosti ili između minimalne i maksimalne vrijednosti. "
"Vrijednosti moraju biti između 1 i 6, a ako je oblik min-max, vrijednost min "
"mora biti niža od maksimalne vrijednosti. Ako je drugačije zadano, "
"&gcompris; se neće pokrenuti."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid "--export-activities-as-sql"
msgstr "--export-activities-as-sql"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid "Export activities as SQL."
msgstr "Izvoz aktivnosti kao SQL."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid "--enable-kioskmode"
msgstr "--enable-kioskmode"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable the kiosk mode (hides Quit and Configuration buttons)."
msgstr "Omogući Kiosk način rada (skriva gumbove Izlaz i Postavke)"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:316
#, no-c-format
msgid "--disable-kioskmode"
msgstr "--disable-kioskmode"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid "Disable the kiosk mode (default)."
msgstr "Onemogući Kiosk način rada (zadano)."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid "--show-home-button"
msgstr "--show-home-button"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show the Home button in the bar (default)."
msgstr "Prikaži Home gumb u traci (zadano)."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:324
#, no-c-format
msgid "--hide-home-button"
msgstr "--hide-home-button"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hide the Home button in the bar."
msgstr "Sakrij Home gumb u traci."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid "--renderer={renderer}"
msgstr "--renderer={renderer}"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specify which graphical renderer to use. On all platforms, “opengl” and "
"software are available. On Windows, you can use “direct3d11” or "
"“direct3d12” (if it was compiled with Qt ≥ 6.6). On &macOS;, you can use "
"“metal”."
msgstr ""
"Navedi koji grafički renderer želiš koristiti. Na svim platformama dostupni "
"su \"opengl\" i softver. Na Windowsima možeš koristiti \"direct3d11\" ili "
"\"direct3d12\" (ako je kompajliran s Qt ≥ 6.6). Na &macOS;, možeš koristiti "
"\"metal\"."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid "--software-renderer"
msgstr "--software-renderer"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use software renderer instead of OpenGL (should work with any graphical "
"card). Deprecated, use “--renderer=software” instead."
msgstr ""
"Koristi softverski renderer umjesto OpenGL-a (trebao bi raditi s bilo kojom "
"grafičkom karticom). Zastarjelo, koristi \"--renderer=software\" umjesto "
"toga."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid "--opengl-renderer"
msgstr "--opengl-renderer"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:337
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use OpenGL renderer instead of software (faster and more graphical effects "
"but can crash with some graphical cards). Deprecated, use “--"
"renderer=opengl” instead."
msgstr ""
"Koristi OpenGL renderer umjesto softvera (brži i bolji grafički efekti, ali "
"može se srušiti s nekim grafičkim karticama). Zastarjelo, koristi \"--"
"renderer=opengl\" umjesto toga."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid "--locale=locale"
msgstr "--locale=locale"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid "Run &gcompris; with the specified locale."
msgstr "Pokreni &gcompris; s specificiranom lokalizacijom."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Windows; Example"
msgstr "&Windows; Primjer"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:349
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can add these switches in the desktop icon properties. Here is an "
"example that runs &gcompris; in kiosk mode in full screen, without "
"Configuration button and cursor:"
msgstr ""
"Navedene opcije možeš dodati u svojstva ikone na radnoj površini. Evo "
"primjera koji pokreće &gcompris; u Kiosk načinu rada na cijelom zaslonu, bez "
"prikaza gumba za konfiguraciju i pokazivača:"

#. Tag: command
#: index.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\"C:\\Program Files\\GCompris-Qt\\bin\\GCompris.exe\" --enable-kioskmode -f -"
"C"
msgstr ""
"\"C:\\Program Files\\GCompris-Qt\\bin\\GCompris.exe\" --enable-kioskmode -f -"
"C"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:354
#, no-c-format
msgid "&GNU;/&Linux; Example"
msgstr "&GNU;/&Linux; Primjer"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:355
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create an application launcher and configure the command line parameters. "
"Here is an example that runs &gcompris; in kiosk mode in fullscreen, without "
"Configuration button and cursor:"
msgstr ""
"Stvara prečac aplikacije i konfigurira parametre naredbenog retka. Evo "
"primjera koji pokreće &gcompris; u Kiosk načinu rada na cijelom zaslonu, bez "
"prikaza gumba za konfiguraciju i pokazivača:"

#. Tag: command
#: index.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid "gcompris-qt --enable-kioskmode -f -C"
msgstr "gcompris-qt --enable-kioskmode -f -C"

